42
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:07,620
Whatever the price
you bought the shares from Rende,

43
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:09,260
I'll buy them back at that same price.

44
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:11,420
Then you'll

45
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,860
withdraw from Huaixiang Group.

46
00:02:14,820 --> 00:02:16,460
But those shares are mine now.

47
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:17,460
Whether or not they get sold

48
