isn't your decision to make.

49
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:23,740
Mr. Biao,

50
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,060
which side are you on?

51
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:27,060
As the Chairman

52
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:29,460
of the Eight Major Cuisines
Culinary Association,

53
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:32,820
I'll handle this matter fairly.

54
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:34,260
I won't favor either party.

55
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:36,940
As you have reached this impasse,

56
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,540
an explanation is needed.

57
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:39,900
I am here

58
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:41,340
to serve as a witness today.

59
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:42,340
Alright.

60
00:02:44,180 --> 00:02:45,820
You said last time you wanted revenge?

61
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:46,620
Here's how.

62
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,300
At the King of Chefs Championship,

63
00:02:48,860 --> 00:02:49,940
if you can win first place

64
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:52,700
and reclaim the title from my father,

65
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:55,300
we'd be glad to leave Huaixiang Group.

66
00:02:55,420 --> 00:02:56,620
What are you thinking?

67
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:59,020
Do you take me for a fool?

68
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:04,060
You think I don't know how your father

69
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,300
won the title at the past championships?

70
