75
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:17,780
How shameless you are!

76
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:18,820
Who are you calling shameless?

77
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:20,900
You!

78
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:23,300
Still setting up schemes and traps?

79
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:25,980
You're too green.

80
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:27,100
If you had the skills,

81
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:28,500
if you could win a world championship

82
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,740
and bring glory to our country,

83
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:31,660
I'd hand over Huaixiang Group to you.

84
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:32,940
But can you?

85
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:34,100
Ms. Tao,

86
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:35,780
don't lower yourself
to arguing with him.

87
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:37,180
What am I?

88
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:39,300
Why would I stoop to his level?

89
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:43,020
Who is being unreasonable?

90
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:46,020
You're insisting
on Mr. Biao as a witness.

91
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:46,780
What's your intention?

92
00:03:47,140 --> 00:03:49,060
Trying to use moral pressure on him?

93
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:50,220
Mr. Biao,

94
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:51,260
you've seen it now.

95
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:53,180
Their conditions

96
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:54,940
are clearly provocative.

97
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,420
No sincerity in their negotiation.

98
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:58,820
And they've put you
in an awkward position

99
00:03:58,820 --> 00:03:59,820
where you can't back down.

100
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,460
I didn't mean to.

101
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:03,340
In my opinion,

102
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,580
you should stay out of this matter.

103
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:06,620
Throw your vote away and abstain.

104
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,260
Let the Zhan family exit
from Huaixiang Group.

105
00:04:10,060 --> 00:04:11,220
Then we can go our separate ways

106
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:12,020
and live our own lives.

107
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:17,460
At least I won't have to work so hard

108
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:18,540
to nurture the company,

109
00:04:18,860 --> 00:04:19,900
only to support you for free.

110
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:20,740
Watch your tongue!

111
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:21,740
What do you mean by for free?

112
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:22,460
Tell me.

113
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:23,740
As a shareholder of Huaixiang Group,

114
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:24,540
what have you done?

115
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,460
I'm being nice by saying that.

116
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:28,940
If you're a man,

117
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:30,820
if you have the guts,

118
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:32,540
