119
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:35,700
Baiwei Group earns a lot every year.

120
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:36,340
What's the matter?

121
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:37,700
Can't they satisfy you?

122
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:40,740
You're eyeing our money.

123
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:42,660
How can you be so greedy?

124
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:44,700
No matter how poor I am,
I don't need you to support me.

125
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:45,740
Well said.

126
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:47,420
As a man, quit Huaixiang Group now.

127
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:48,300
Don't let me support you.

128
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:56,860
Shikun,

129
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:57,900
sit down.

130
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,100
Zhan Jun?

131
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,900
What Ms. Too said makes sense.

132
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:13,260
Ms. Tao,

133
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,060
please share your thoughts.

134
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,060
I don't think you would let

135
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,220
the title go to someone else.

136
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,380
We're not aiming

137
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,500
for the top spot.

138
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,260
Let's settle on a reasonable ranking.

139
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:28,940
If Qiao Zhi can achieve this ranking,

140
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:30,700
you'll withdraw your shares.

141
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:32,220
And every penny I owe you

142
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:34,580
will be paid in full.

143
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:35,340
After all,

144
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:37,460
