149
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,100
Are you blind?

150
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,420
Didn't you see there's a zero here?

151
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:57,460
The top 30?

152
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,820
You think you can fool me?

153
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:00,860
What can I do?

154
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:02,180
This is all the capability I have.

155
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:03,860
Don't want to negotiate anymore?

156
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:05,340
Then you can leave.

157
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,180
Grandpa, see this?

158
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,300
They are going to abstain.

159
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:07,940
Alright then.

160
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:09,820
Sign the resolution

161
00:06:09,820 --> 00:06:10,380
