162
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:11,100
now.

163
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:11,900
Once you sign it,

164
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:13,820
I'll come to your house tonight
and cook you a delicious meal.

165
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:14,100
You…

166
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:14,660
Top two?

167
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:15,660
No way.

168
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:16,460
Top 28.

169
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,700
Top three?

170
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:19,220
Can the top three work?

171
00:06:19,340 --> 00:06:20,460
Top 23 would be about right.

172
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:21,220
Top four?

173
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:22,340
Four is no good either.

174
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:23,740
At most, at most top 14.

175
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:24,700
Top five.

176
00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:26,940
What's the difference
between the top four and five?

177
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:27,860
Top six at least.

178
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:28,980
Otherwise, let's stop talking.

179
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:30,220
Alright,

180
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:32,020
top six it is.

181
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:33,660
Grandpa,

182
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,220
