183
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:37,100
Say a word for me.

184
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,460
Oh, come on!

185
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:40,860
Stop complaining.

186
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:42,060
Bite me if you can!

187
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,620
Alright.

188
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,020
Since

189
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,380
everyone has agreed,

190
00:06:48,340 --> 00:06:48,940
let's follow the old rule.

191
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:50,340
Tea time.

192
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:09,300
Well done.

193
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,780
You surprised me.

194
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:14,180
You said we should talk properly.

195
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:15,660
I was talking properly.

196
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:17,820
Alright then.

197
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,020
By the way, Mom,

198
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:19,940
there's something

199
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:20,780
I need to ask of you.

200
00:07:20,980 --> 00:07:21,460
Go ahead.

201
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:24,220
The Zhan family will play tricks.

202
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:25,300
Please help me

203
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:26,660
