204
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:29,860
At this point,

205
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:31,780
they'll pull some ruthless moves

206
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:33,300
beyond your imagination.

207
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:35,500
Don't worry.

208
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:36,860
I have an ace up my sleeve.

209
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:41,420
Are you really only 25?

210
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,180
Look a bit too mature for my age!

211
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,060
Interesting.

212
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,280
[Mr. Xu]

213
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:23,020
That's quite a catch!

214
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:25,700
Why didn't you call me?

215
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:27,740
