216
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:29,300
Boss!

217
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:30,740
Boss!

218
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:31,980
Boss!

219
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:36,620
Eight hundred!

220
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:41,380
You're so generous!

221
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:42,460
Thanks a lot!

222
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:47,980
Keep on fishing!

223
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:49,060
Alright.

224
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:50,460
Looks like you've made your money back.

225
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:51,860
Enjoy the thrill.

226
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:52,700
Sit down.

227
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:55,740
I heard

228
