in the championship tomorrow.

229
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:00,340
How are you preparing?

230
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:01,340
Not bad.

231
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:04,100
After being kicked out by Nanfang,

232
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,220
besides traveling around

233
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:07,940
and eating and drinking,

234
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:10,540
I still enjoy fishing.

235
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:12,780
In this circle,

236
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:13,820
there's a game

237
00:09:14,420 --> 00:09:15,380
called fishing pond betting.

238
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:17,620
Pay to enter the fishpond.

239
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:18,980
Then, whatever number of fish you catch,

240
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:20,660
sell them back to the owner

241
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:22,380
at a certain market price ratio.

242
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:23,700
I've heard about it.

243
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,460
Later, gradually, people started

244
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,900
marking a price on each fish,

245
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:29,620
and the amounts kept getting bigger,

246
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,740
turning it into disguised gambling.

247
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:32,660
But this

248
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,100
is against the law.

249
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:35,380
I want to remind you

250
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:37,540
that there's gambling

251
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,820
going on behind the scenes
of the championship.

252
00:09:39,180 --> 00:09:40,180
So, you mean

253
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,700
I'm tagged.

254
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:45,220
Anyway, be careful.

255
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:47,460
When they get so obsessed with gambling

256
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:49,140
that they'll do anything.

257
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:51,580
I see.

258
00:09:52,180 --> 00:09:53,300
You specifically called me here

259
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,460
to remind me.

260
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:56,140
Thank you very much.

261
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:57,980
You can't afford to lose.

262
00:09:58,420 --> 00:09:59,580
You are this family's hope.

263
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:01,940
If it weren't for your reminder,

264
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:03,780
I might have fallen into their trap.

265
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:07,060
It was just a small favor.

266
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:09,940
Dad,

267
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:11,260
come back.

268
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:13,180
This family needs you.

269
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,380
Having you here is enough.

270
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:19,780
Dad,

271
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,260
actually,

272
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:23,260
I think Mom still cares about you.

273
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:25,020
Only you can cheer her up.

274
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:27,300
You're still young.

275
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,100
You wouldn't understand yet

276
00:10:29,540 --> 00:10:31,060
what brings true happiness

277
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:32,420
to a man at his 50s.

278
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:35,060
Great.

279
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:42,140
This one is good.

280
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:43,980
Dad, can I have this fish?

281
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:44,860
I'll cook it for Mom later.

282
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:45,980
I...

283
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:48,140
I was thinking of trading it for a meal.

284
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:49,900
Choose.

285
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:51,220
Keep it,

286
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:52,220
or let me cook it

287
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:53,180
so Mom can enjoy something fresh.

288
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:55,660
Take it away.

289
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:57,860
She can't handle pepper!

290
00:10:58,620 --> 00:10:59,060
Alright.

